Displays a window in which you specify the folder,
name, and format of a file for saving the current
icon.

Use this option when you want to convert an icon
to a different file format.  Icon Editor writes
these formats:  XView Icon, X Bitmap, Color X 
Pixmap, and Mono Pixmap.

