:ViewButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/iconedit.handbook
View

The View menu toggles from Grid On to Grid Off:

Grid On	turns on a 4-pixel grid for the canvas.

Grid Off turns off the grid.	

The grid is useful for aligning and centering
all or part of your icon.

:GridMenuItem:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/iconedit.handbook
