:MoveLeftButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/iconedit.handbook
Left Arrow

Moves the icon or selected region one pixel to
the left.

If you move the image off the canvas, pixels are
cropped. They are not restored if you move the
image back.

:MoveRightButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/iconedit.handbook
Right Arrow

Moves the icon or selected region one pixel to
